@startuml checkout_flow
participant Customer
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant Database

Customer -> Frontend: Add items to cart
Customer -> Frontend: Proceed to checkout
Frontend -> Backend: POST /orders
Backend -> Database: Get cart items
Database --> Backend: Items returned
Backend -> Database: Begin transaction
Backend -> Database: Create order record
Backend -> Database: Insert order items
Backend -> Database: Clear cart
Backend -> Database: Commit transaction
Backend --> Frontend: 201 Created + Order
Frontend -> Customer: Order confirmation

@enduml
